# Documentation Discipline

- Treat `Documentation/` as maintained source of truth.
- Keep confirmed requirements, assumptions, and open questions clearly separated.
- Update `Documentation/feature-tracker.md` when scope/status/dependency changes.
- Update `Documentation/decision-log.md` when decisions are made or unresolved questions emerge.
- If only one canonical document changes, explain why related docs did not need updates.
